***********************************************************************
The 0.1.5.1 release was compiled under:
  * Archlinux
  * Manjaro 0.9
  * Debian Jesse
  * Debian Buster
  * Crunchbang "Waldorf"

***********************************************************************

o System requirements for 0.1:
    Required: FLTK >= 1.3.1
              g++ >= 4.7

o Compile and install:
    1. Just type:
       $ make
       the binary is in ./bin/

    If you have compiled it under other platforms, or failed to
  compile, please tell me.
